{"tid":882643,"cid":18,"subCid":0,"title":"有冇發覺Google親醫學資訊都似Content farm多?","createTime":"2018-10-30T09:24:19.000Z","updateTime":"2018-10-30T09:38:08.000Z","uid":65139,"like":4,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"d7d71dd95c8bc4e1e2f7c323b73b733b5b33d61e","tid":882643,"uid":65139,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-30T09:24:19.000Z","msg":"繼智能手機有冇令人變戇鳩之後, 醒起另一個現象想大家討論下...歡迎鳩噏<br />\n<br />\n如題, 似乎好多人頭暈身興都會想上網搵下資料(唔計問連登醫生...), 始終畏疾忌醫都係好平常嘅心態<br />\n<br />\n但有冇發覺, Google親任何病徵, 結果都係出啲咩人人健康網, 健康咩柒網, 保健至叻星咁果類所謂&quot;健康資訊網&quot;...其實根本似係Content farm多<br />\n<br />\n入面啲文大同少異, 以中醫內容居多(利伸小弟會睇中醫), 但又毫無註腳/Reference...有時仲會Quote幾個病人Online問症同埋個&quot;醫師&quot;嘅鳩噏回應咁<br />\n<br />\n相對Search其他內容, 例如問d technical野, financial news, 當然rumor都多, 但content farm好似比較少見<br />\n<br />\n因為某類資料demand高? information asymmetry嚴重啲?"},{"pid":"4a5cc2262c845a55252fc7e6d6465dc96badc5a4","tid":882643,"uid":60470,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-10-30T09:26:48.000Z","msg":"搵其他野，頭幾條都成日係啲咩壹讀、每日頭條<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\nGoogle<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3a60ac8f464f3377dfcb89d0cd217f5740e694ca","tid":882643,"uid":65139,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"4a5cc2262c845a55252fc7e6d6465dc96badc5a4","tid":882643,"uid":60470,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-10-30T09:26:48.000Z","msg":"搵其他野，頭幾條都成日係啲咩壹讀、每日頭條<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\nGoogle<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-30T09:28:22.000Z","msg":"呢兩個垃圾網點解過到Google個fact check<br />\n<br />\n(好似之前話implement咗, true news會剔/置頂?)"},{"pid":"e9fd790f8e7034b2a22f3667ac33624e0051deb3","tid":882643,"uid":36296,"like":0,"dislike":3,"score":-3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-10-30T09:30:08.000Z","msg":"因為真正醫學文章 普通人唔識搵加睇唔明？"},{"pid":"fa97bf6746d0d9cfa90e1a5336d5274571b0572b","tid":882643,"uid":126100,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-30T09:32:57.000Z","msg":"因為醫生唔用電腦做 analysis<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n明明可以整個 system 將D symptoms 入晒落去已經做到好準既分析，但因為要保持自己權威<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"534da09b6b302ca2154529983f2ec1eff498d9dc","tid":882643,"uid":31254,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-30T09:34:23.000Z","msg":"因為中文唔係知識嘅載體<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n用英文搵好多時都冇呢個問題"},{"pid":"6da4878d4a54e5cec13b653dc066785618253647","tid":882643,"uid":26506,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-30T09:35:15.000Z","msg":"English motherfucker, do you search it?"},{"pid":"42c4682efd3b9e7998234cabc6e9881328916aee","tid":882643,"uid":176063,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-30T09:35:31.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"37fb1f8bd710f7261f8e097ce1d1b91c895256d0","tid":882643,"uid":26506,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"e9fd790f8e7034b2a22f3667ac33624e0051deb3","tid":882643,"uid":36296,"like":0,"dislike":3,"score":-3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-10-30T09:30:08.000Z","msg":"因為真正醫學文章 普通人唔識搵加睇唔明？"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-30T09:38:08.000Z","msg":"講緊語言定內容？你睇 Mayo Clinic 甚至WebMD有冇噉難明？"}]}